Package: omia
Title: Epidemiological and Statistical Workflows for Outbreak Analysis
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Kana Contributor [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Kana Contributor <kana@example.com>
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Kana",
           family = "Contributor",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "kana@example.com")
Description: Tools for preparing incidence data, estimating time-varying
    reproduction numbers, fitting growth models, comparing incidence models,
    uncertainty-aware simulation/forecasting, and reproducible forecast
    evaluation.
